verifier to verify exhaustivity/negativity of (image, noun phrase) pairs, as the AI verification step in Fig. 5.
SA-Co/HQ-Food: PL-Food is cleaned by human verifiers for both MV and EV tasks. For non-exhaustive
datapoints after EV, human annotators further manually correct them, as the “Correct” step in Fig. 5.
