state-of-the-art methodsRen et al.(2024a);Wu et al.(2024b);Xu et al.( 2023 );Zhang et al.(2022b). We
report mean BoxAP averaged across all 13 datasets, with SAM 3 consistently achieving superior performance
and establishing new state-of-the-art results. Complete dataset-specific results for each OdinW13 dataset are
provided inFig. 20b.
